President Barack Obama has issued a memorandum designating the National Science and Technology Council (NSTC) to coordinate certain activities under the Arctic Research and Policy Act of 1984. The NSTC will be responsible for coordinating activities assigned to the Interagency Arctic Research Policy Committee, including through committees of the NSTC. The memorandum authorizes and directs the Director of the Office of Science and Technology Policy to publish this memorandum in the Federal Register.